Magenta Therapeutics, Inc., herein referred to as the "Company," may terminate this agreement at any time for cause, but in no event shall it terminate without cause unless such termination does not materially and adversely affect the interests of the non-terminating party. In the event that the Company chooses to exercise its right to terminate, it shall provide the other party with a written notice of at least 30 days prior to the effective date of termination, which may be extended by mutual agreement in writing. The non-terminating party understands that the Company's ability to terminate for cause is a fundamental aspect of this agreement.
